response.overview: The "Figure-Bodied" Shihono Ryo, with her intellectual features and delicate, girl-like frame, takes on the challenge of "life-sized" sexiness. Everything is beautiful—from her long, slender legs extending from a tight skirt to her elegant fingertips playing with her stockings. Featuring her first-ever daring backless scene and covering everything from cute costumes to mature "older sister" looks, this is an indisputable masterpiece! ☆
response.title: しほの涼 Precious
